lead_paragraph: A Delaware bankruptcy judge is weighing a request by Trump Entertainment Resorts to get out of its pension obligations under a collective bargaining agreement with union workers at the Taj Mahal casino in Atlantic City, New Jersey.

headline.main: Judge Eyes Trump Entertainment Pension Obligations
